This is a very simple step by step application wizard.
Including create tables and users.
Included in this project:
DataMapper ORM for CodeIgniter (http://wanwizard.eu/categories/Datamapper)
Simple_Auth for CodeIgniter by Greg Aker (https://bitbucket.org/gaker/codeigniter-simple-auth)
Hierarchical MVC for CodeIgniter (https://bitbucket.org/wiredesignz/codeigniter-modular-extensions-hmvc/wiki/Home)
Required:
PHP 5.xx
MySQL
Web Server

Note:
1. Create a database 
2. These files should be writable :
 a. Application/config/database.php
 b. Application/config/config.php
 c. Application/config/autoload.php

